!----------------------
! Get RGB values on interval 0-100 from hexa color code
go set_rgb_from_hexa ($02)

!----------------------
! Define 
ppl color ($01),`RRR`,`GGG`,`BBB`

!----------------------
cancel var RRR,GGG,BBB

!----------------------
set mode/last verify
